title: Retailer Torrid cancels plans for initial public offering
text: Plus-sized women's apparel retailer Torrid Inc. pulled its plans for an initial public offering late Friday, according to a filing with the Securities and Exchange Commission.

title: Restaurants are investing in photogenic decor to attract Instagram users
text: Restaurants took note of the free marketing possibilities and are now making more expensive investments — from customized tiles to handmade tables.

title: A Little Diesel Helps Lion8 Electric Truck Conquer The Cold
text: The Lion8 boasts cold-weather performance fitting to the Class 8 electric truck's Canadian origins – only a 10 percent reduction in range even in sub-zero temperatures.

title: Earnings and data could be proof that slowdown fears were overblown
text: Earnings season shifts into a higher gear, as investors also watch for fresh economic data that could show that the economy is pulling out of a temporary rut.
